data.description: Elegant Family Retreat in Poinciana  Address: 656 Milan Drive, Kissimmee, FL 34758   Nestled within the serene community of Poinciana, this exquisite family retreat offers an unparalleled blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Boasting meticulous craftsmanship and modern amenities, this residence presents a remarkable opportunity to embrace the quintessential Florida lifestyle.  Interior Features: Upon entering, you are greeted by an inviting foyer leading to the expansive formal living and dinning area adorned with soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. Adjacent to the kitchen, the family dining area offers seamless transitions for entertaining guests.  Upstairs luxurious master suite is a private oasis, complete with a spacious his and Hers walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom featuring, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. Three additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests and or the rest of the family.  Outdoor Oasis: Step outside to discover your own private oasis. The overlooks the lush backyard, offering the perfect setting for al fresco dining or simply unwinding amidst the tranquil surroundings. The expansive yard provides ample space for outdoor activities and gardening enthusiasts or a place for your own private pool. Plus a large 10x20 storage shed for added storage.   Additional Features:       Tile flooring throughout the main living areas for easy maintenance.       Plus engineered hardwood upstairs  Lots of windows enhance natural light and reduce utility costs.  Laundry room with washer and dryer for added convenience.  close proximity to shopping, hospital, dining, community pools, playground major highways   Conveniently situated in Poinciana, residents enjoy easy access to great schools, and recreational attractions. Explore nearby destinations such as Walt Disney World Resort, Universal Studios, and SeaWorld Orlando, all within a short drive.   Embrace the epitome of Florida living with this stunning family retreat. Schedule your viewing today and make 656 Milan Drive your new home!
